Life
</a>
</h6>
<a class="serif med" href="http://www.theglobeandmail.com/life/health/new-health/conditions/weight-loss/is-rob-fords-weight-loss-goal-realistic/article2305054/" title="Jan 17, 2012 9:30AM EST - Yesterday Toronto Mayor Rob Ford publically declared his goal to shed 50 pounds by June 18th" name="&lpos=Widget - Article Related Content - Today's Must Reads&lid=3" onClick="s_objectID='';">Is Rob Ford&rsquo;s weight-loss goal realistic?</a>
